            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Dianae Reginae <expan><abbr>Aurel</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Titus <expan><abbr>vexill</abbr><ex>arius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>uitum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>I <expan><abbr>Ital</abbr><ex>icae</ex></expan> Gordianae <expan><abbr>Au</abbr><ex>gustae</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">in</supplied> <expan><abbr>reg</abbr><ex>ione</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Mont</abbr><ex>anensium</ex></expan> cu<supplied reason="lost">m</supplied> <lb n="5"/>suis ex voto <expan><abbr>pos</abbr><ex>uit</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Pilaster. Z. 1-5 befinden sich auf dem Kapitell; darunter ein eingetieftes Bildfeld mit einer sitzenden und schreibenden Figur; unter dem Bildfeld Z. 6 und noch der Kopf einer Merkurdarstellung.</p>
            </div>
